{"model": "ep-20260508213828-7ntjl", "input": [{"type": "message", "role": "user", "content": [{"type": "input_audio", "file_id": "file-20260610003140-67rn8"}, {"type": "input_text", "text": "你是短视频声音设计师。分析音频里的音乐、音效、节奏和情绪，不要重点转写人声。\n把声音拆成若干可迁移的节奏片段。start_time 和 end_time 使用秒，统一保留小数点后一位。"}]}], "text": {"format": {"type": "json_schema", "name": "music_ir", "strict": true, "schema": {"type": "object", "properties": {"parts": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "properties": {"start_time": {"type": "number", "description": "片段开始时间，单位秒，保留小数点后一位。"}, "end_time": {"type": "number", "description": "片段结束时间，单位秒，保留小数点后一位。"}, "description": {"type": "string", "description": "片段内容和可迁移作用。"}}, "required": ["start_time", "end_time", "description"], "additionalProperties": false}, "description": "音乐或声音片段列表。"}}, "required": ["parts"], "additionalProperties": false}}}}